                        <row rowsep="1">
                            <entry>
                                <para>1.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Off/On</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Disconnect connector (400) from the ECM. Turn key ON. At (400) use test lead to
                                    jumper terminal 22 to gnd. Is red engine warning light ON?
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>&#160;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>&#160;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Have Caterpillar dealer diagnose ECM operation.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Locate open or poor connection in circuit 97AT between connectors (423) and (400),
                                    then repair.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
